 Interface Unit, and key loading panel with a modern computing architecture and permanent ancillary equipment. The modification will simplify the design, enable ethernet loading of mission software, allow for
 back up radio cryptographic key loading, combat obsolete data transfer medium, and drive non-mission capable rates down by 900+ hours per year. Without this modification, aircraft project to be grounded$$, $$$$, $$Exhibit P-40, Budget Line Item Justification: PB 2027 Air Force                                                                                                                                     Date: April 2026
