 Joint Strike Fighter (JSF) program will enhance and field a family of aircraft that meets the needs of DoW and allies with three air vehicle variants including: the F-35A Conventional Take Off and Landing
 (CTOL) variant, the F-35B Short Take-Off and Vertical Landing (STOVL) variant, and the F-35C Carrier Variant (CV) delivering commonality among the three variants to minimize life cycle costs. This is a joint
